      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable paint chips on the hood, a few minor door dings, and some light scuffing on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining on the carpets and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will soon require a standard brake service and the air conditioning takes a moment to reach full cooling capacity. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
