    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here; it's just pristine. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
