    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the critical rod bearing service has been performed, and the rear subframe carrier panel has been reinforced to prevent common fatigue failure. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-correct geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in and tactile feedback these cars are known for. The exterior retains its factory-original depth with no orange peel or clear coat degradation, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A turn-key machine for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
